		<h2 class="section-header">
		<a href="http://news.instyle.com"><span>What&rsquo;s <em>right</em> Now!</span></a>
	</h2>
	
	<div class="wrn-detail-wrapper">

	
				<div class="col1">

					<article class="post-308740 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-beauty category-beauty-brands category-channel-makeup category-holiday-shopping category-lips category-makeup category-prada category-shopping category-valentino article-story">

						<header>

							<a href="http://www.instyle.com/instyle/package/general/0,,20255274,00.html" class=" sponsor-tag slug-makeup">Valentine&#039;s Day</a>
							<h1 class="article-title">Valentine&#8217;s Day Gift Guide:&nbsp;Beauty</h1>

							<div class="hero">
									<a href="http://www.instyle.com/gallery/valentines-day-gift-guide-beauty"><div class="post-image-container"><img class="full" src="http://img2.timeinc.net/instyle/images/2015/GALLERY/020315-v-day-beauty-lead-594.jpg" width="594" height="594" alt="Valentine&#039;s Day Beauty" /></div></a><a href="http://www.instyle.com/gallery/valentines-day-gift-guide-beauty" class="btn-see-photos"><i class="icon-gallery"></i> See All Photos <i class="icon-arrowright"></i></a><span class="wp-credit-text">Courtesy</span>							</div>

								<cite>
		<time datetime="2015-02-08T16:32:39+00:00">February 8, 2015 @ 4:32 pm</time>			<div class="byline">By: <a href="http://news.instyle.com/author/sarahewalter/">Sarah Walter</a></div>
			</cite>
	
						</header>

						<div class="article-wrapper">

							<div class="col1">
											<div id="module-share-tools-sticky-wrapper"><div id="module-share-tools-sticky-wrapper-inner">
				<section class="module-share-tools">
					<ul>
						<li class="share-count"><i class="icon icon-share"></i><span><div data-share-url="http://news.instyle.com/2015/02/08/valentines-day-gift-guide-beauty/">Share</div></span></li>
						<li><a target="_blank" data-share-headline="Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Gift%20Guide%3A%20Beauty" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.instyle.com%2F2015%2F02%2F08%2Fvalentines-day-gift-guide-beauty%2F&amp;p=Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Gift%20Guide%3A%20Beauty" class="share-popup share-facebook"><i class="icon icon-gallery_facebook"></i></a></li>
						<li><a target="_blank" data-share-headline="Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Gift%20Guide%3A%20Beauty" href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.instyle.com%2F2015%2F02%2F08%2Fvalentines-day-gift-guide-beauty%2F&amp;media=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.timeinc.net%2Finstyle%2Fimages%2F2015%2FGALLERY%2F020315-v-day-beauty-lead-594.jpg&amp;description=Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Gift%20Guide%3A%20Beauty %20%23InStyle" class="share-popup share-pinterest"><i class="icon icon-gallery_pinterest"></i></a></li>
						<li><a target="_blank" data-share-headline="Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Gift%20Guide%3A%20Beauty" href="https://twitter.com/share?text=Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Gift%20Guide%3A%20Beauty @InStyle&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.instyle.com%2F2015%2F02%2F08%2Fvalentines-day-gift-guide-beauty%2F&amp;related=InStyle" class="share-popup share-twitter"><i class="icon icon-twitter"></i></a></li>
						<li><a target="_blank" data-share-headline="Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Gift%20Guide%3A%20Beauty" href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.instyle.com%2F2015%2F02%2F08%2Fvalentines-day-gift-guide-beauty%2F" class="share-popup share-googleplus"><i class="icon icon-googleplus"></i></a></li>
					</ul>
				</section>
				<div class="fave-this"><a href="http://news.instyle.com/2015/02/08/valentines-day-gift-guide-beauty/"  data-share-headline="Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Gift%20Guide%3A%20Beauty" class="fave-this-btn"><i class="icon icon-fave-animation icon-faved"></i><i class="icon icon-fave"></i></a></div>

			</div></div>
									</div>

							<div class="col2">

								<div class="article-body">
									
<p><span class="dropcap">T</span>he stakes are upped for the most important date night of the year, but coupled up or flying solo, we’ve got the beauty picks that will help you feel your most beautiful (and last long past the dozen roses and chocolate). Skip conventional red polish for NCLA’S cute <a href="http://www.instyle.com/gallery/valentines-day-gift-guide-beauty/page3">heart lacquers</a> in shades like “Heart Attack” and “XOXO,” or if you’re really looking to spice things up, look no further than <a href="http://www.instyle.com/gallery/valentines-day-gift-guide-beauty/page13">Make Up For Ever</a>’s <em>Fifty Shades of Grey</em>-inspired makeup kit. Shop our picks for a pamper-filled day, or better yet, send our compilation to your significant other for a not-so-subtle hint!</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.instyle.com/gallery/valentines-day-gift-guide-beauty">PHOTOS: The best beauty gifts to give (and receive) this Valentine&#8217;s Day!</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.instyle.com/holidays-occasions/valentines-day/valentines-day-gift-guide-lifestyle-0">RELATED: Valentine&#8217;s Day Gift Guide: Lifestyle</a></strong></p>
								</div>

